### Search for .NET jobs in Richmond
GET https://localhost:{port}/api/jobs/search?keywords=.net+developer&location=Richmond,+VA&radiusMiles=30

### Search for C# jobs, wider radius
GET https://localhost:{port}/api/jobs/search?keywords=c%23+developer&location=Richmond,+VA&radiusMiles=50

### Search for senior engineering roles
GET https://localhost:{port}/api/jobs/search?keywords=senior+software+engineer&location=Richmond,+VA&radiusMiles=25